The fifth largest cryptocurrency in the market in terms of market capitalization, Litecoin (LTC), is having an amazing bull run, recording its one - month high at $231 as of the time of posting. LTC has recovered by over 100% from its huge dip to $106 last February 6. Furthermore, LTC's market capitalization has once again reached the $10 billion for the first time since January 29..
