The Litecoin Cash Controversy.
`__ 1_______ `___ `___________ 
Litecoin's seemingly magical run is a bit questionable for analysts due to some controversy surrounding the news for the supposed upcoming fork, "Litecoin Cash (LCC)." According to the LCC official website, existing LTC holders at block 1,371,111 will receive 10 LCC tokens for every 1 LTC. This news may have had an influence in Litecoin's current bull run..
1_________ `________ `______ `__ `_ ` `__ `___________ `__ `_______ `__ `_ `___ `__________ `__________ `__ `___ `__ `__ `_______ `_______ `____ 1________ `___ `______ `________ `_ `__ `__ `_______ `_______ `_______ `__ `______ `_ `____ `________ `___ `______ `_ `__ `_____ `__ `____ ` `___ `___ `___ `__ `___ `__ `_ `________ `_ 1_________ `______ `___ `____ 
However, Litecoin founder and creator Charlie Lee, together with the Litecoin community, have called this project a scam, dismissing the news as mere propaganda to confuse Litecoin investors. The people behind the LCC project may have gotten their inspiration from a similar fork event that happened with Bitcoin last year..
